CB->paramHasNonNullAttr(ArgIdx, /*AllowUndefOrPoison=*/false))\n      return
!PtrValueMayBeModified;\n  }\nThis preserves existing semantics for
pointer-typed arguments and avoids calling paramHasNonNullAttr for
